                                  <node-reference>
                                    <axis>[federated.1w4my0d11xnlwb1gzdsi10l8qcvk].[avg:adr:qk]</axis>
                                  </node-reference>
                                </y-coord>
                                <page-reference />
                              </visual-coordinate>
                            </point>
                            <body x='-9' y='-220' />
                          </annotation>
                        </annotations>
                      </worksheet>
                    </capturedDeltas>
                  </story-point>
                  <story-point caption='The ADR distribution is concentrated near the portfolio average of approximately $105, while a smaller number of premium-priced bookings create a long upper pricing tail. City hotels show a wider ADR distribution and higher booking frequency compared to resort properties, indicating stronger pricing flexibility across urban locations.' captured-sheet='ADR Distribution by Hotel' id='13' />
                  <story-point caption='Conclusion' captured-sheet='' id='14' />
                  <story-point captured-sheet='' id='15' />
                </story-points>
              </flipboard>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='66000' id='6' story-point-id='14' type-v2='text' w='73714' x='8500' y='28000'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000'>Conclusion</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000'>* Avalon Hotels generated strong booking activity and stable ADR performance across multiple customer segments. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000'>* Online bookings emerged as the largest revenue-driving segment but also carried elevated cancellation risk and pricing variability. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000'>* Seasonal demand patterns, booking lead times, and customer behaviors significantly influenced both ADR performance and reservation stability. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000'>* Direct bookings and medium-length stays demonstrated stronger pricing opportunities and more consistent revenue potential. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000'>* Data visualization and segmentation analysis revealed clear opportunities to optimize pricing, marketing focus, and operational planning.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='68700' hidden='true' id='7' story-point-id='15' type-v2='text' w='71429' x='11643' y='19500'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000'>Strategic Recommendations</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000'>Strengthen targeted retention and cancellation mitigation strategies for high-risk Online booking channels. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000'>Expand premium pricing and loyalty incentives for Direct booking customers to improve long-term revenue stability. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000'>Leverage seasonal ADR trends to optimize dynamic pricing during peak demand periods. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000'>Encourage medium and extended stay bookings through bundled offers and promotional packages. </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000'>Continue using dashboard-driven monitoring to support real-time pricing, occupancy, and revenue decision-making.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{CD8D4CCB-D76D-416F-B8B1-F9003A51B2BA}' />
    </dashboard>
